 * 2. Using a HashMap to group lexemes with identical sorted characters
 * 3. Filtering and returning only groups with multiple anagrams
 * 
 * @param lexemes Input array of strings to be analyzed for anagrams
 * @return Array of anagram groups, where each group contains multiple anagrammatic lexemes
